entries.femaleVariant: Hey, where'd you disappear to yesterday?
Oh, took the kid to an interview at Clouds.
Ooh, aiming high. How'd it go?
Well, the gonk battered her with questions the whole damn day, only to say her legs were too short.
Ugh, what an ass! How long's it take to see what sort of legs are in front of you?
'Zackly. Anyway, girl's upset. Wanted to get outta here... Says at least it doesn't smell there, plus there's no Wraiths.
